---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>

  <!-- ===== NAV ===== -->
  <nav id="nav" class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 transition-all duration-300" style="background: transparent;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
        NGM<span style="color: #D4AF37;">.</span>
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://notbadlah.com" class="hidden sm:inline text-sm" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">
          ← Part-time first? Try RintiZ
        </a>
        <a href="#apply"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold transition-all duration-200 hover:opacity-90"
          style="background: #D4AF37; color: #0C1B33;">
          Apply Now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section id="hero" style="background: #0C1B33; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">

    <!-- Background texture -->
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 70% 50%, rgba(212,175,55,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%);pointer-events:none;"></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(212,175,55,0.3),transparent);"></div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 w-full" style="padding-top: 120px; padding-bottom: 80px;">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

        <!-- Left: Headline + CTA -->
        <div id="hero-left">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-8" style="background: rgba(212,175,55,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.25); border-radius: 999px; padding: 6px 16px; width: fit-content;">
            <span style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#D4AF37;display:inline-block;"></span>
            <span style="font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:600;color:#D4AF37;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;">AIA Elite Academy · Next Gen Millionaire</span>
          </div>

          <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); line-height: 1.06; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 24px;">
            Your full-time career<br/>
            in financial planning.<br/>
            <span style="color: #D4AF37;">The income is real.</span>
          </h1>

          <p style="font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.6vw, 1.1rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 420px;">
            NGM is AIA Malaysia's structured full-time programme with monthly bonuses on top of commission — tracked, paid, and guaranteed by contract. From Month 1.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="#apply" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-sm transition-all hover:scale-105" style="background: #D4AF37; color: #0C1B33;">
              Apply Now — it's free
            </a>
            <a href="#bonus" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm transition-all hover:opacity-80" style="border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: #ffffff;">
              See the bonus structure ↓
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 mt-12" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding-top: 28px;">
            <div>
              <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #D4AF37; font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">24 months</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 2px;">structured support</div>
            </div>
            <div style="width:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);"></div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #D4AF37; font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">RM16,000</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 2px;">max monthly bonus (M1–M6)</div>
            </div>
            <div style="width:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);"></div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #D4AF37; font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">+Quarterly</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 2px;">bonuses stack on top</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Big stat card -->
        <div id="hero-right" class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
          <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.2); border-radius: 24px; padding: clamp(28px,4vw,48px); max-width: 380px; width: 100%;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom: 12px;">At the top tier</p>
            <div style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.5rem); font-weight: 800; color: #D4AF37; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px;" class="tabular">RM16,000</div>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-bottom: 28px;">monthly bonus, Months 1–6<br/>On top of your sales commission.</p>

            <div style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding-top: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span style="font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">AFYC required</span>
                <span style="font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff;" class="tabular">RM12,000/month</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span style="font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Cases required</span>
                <span style="font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff;">3 per month</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span style="font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Programme</span>
                <span style="font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 600; color: #D4AF37;">NGM — AIA Elite Academy</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); line-height: 1.6;">Lower tiers available from RM3,500 AFYC. Bonuses paid 15th of the following month via GIRO.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== WHO QUALIFIES ===== -->
  <section id="qualify" class="py-24 px-6" style="background: #ffffff;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="fade-up text-center mb-16">
        <p style="color:#D4AF37;font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;">Entry Requirements</p>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); color: #111; line-height: 1.15;">Do you qualify?</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: #777; margin-top: 12px; max-width: 480px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">NGM is open to new applicants and to those converting from RintiZ. Here's what you need.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Two paths -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">

        <!-- New Application -->
        <div class="fade-up card p-8">
          <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#f0f0f0;border-radius:999px;padding:5px 14px;margin-bottom:24px;">
            <span style="font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:#555;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;">New Application</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div style="width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#0C1B33;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">
                <svg width="10" height="8" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 4L3.5 6.5L9 1" stroke="#D4AF37" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600;color:#111;font-size:0.9rem;">Age 21 to 55</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div style="width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#0C1B33;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">
                <svg width="10" height="8" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 4L3.5 6.5L9 1" stroke="#D4AF37" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600;color:#111;font-size:0.9rem;">Minimum Diploma</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#777;margin-top:2px;">Or 3 years working experience in any field</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div style="width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#0C1B33;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">
                <svg width="10" height="8" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 4L3.5 6.5L9 1" stroke="#D4AF37" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600;color:#111;font-size:0.9rem;">RM3,000+ monthly income</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#777;margin-top:2px;">Proof of income required (past 3 months or 1 year)</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div style="width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#0C1B33;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">
                <svg width="10" height="8" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 4L3.5 6.5L9 1" stroke="#D4AF37" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600;color:#111;font-size:0.9rem;">Panel interview</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#777;margin-top:2px;">Successful completion required before commencement</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Converting from RintiZ -->
        <div class="fade-up card p-8" style="border-color: #D4AF37; background: #fffdf5;">
          <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#fef9e0;border-radius:999px;padding:5px 14px;margin-bottom:24px;">
            <span style="font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:#b8900a;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;">Converting from RintiZ</span>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-bottom: 20px;">Already in RintiZ part-time? Convert to NGM once you hit:</p>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div style="width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#D4AF37;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">
                <svg width="10" height="8" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 4L3.5 6.5L9 1" stroke="#0C1B33" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:700;color:#111;font-size:0.9rem;">AFYC RM9,000 + 9 cases</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#777;margin-top:2px;">Within your coded month (M0) + first 6 months</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div style="width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#D4AF37;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">
                <svg width="10" height="8" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 4L3.5 6.5L9 1" stroke="#0C1B33" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:700;color:#111;font-size:0.9rem;">Persistency Rate D0 90%, D1 85%</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#777;margin-top:2px;">Policies must stay active</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div style="width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#D4AF37;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">
                <svg width="10" height="8" viewBox="0 0 10 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 4L3.5 6.5L9 1" stroke="#0C1B33" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:700;color:#111;font-size:0.9rem;">Within rolling past 3 months</div>
                <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#777;margin-top:2px;">Conversion window: rolling 3-month AFYC</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://notbadlah.com" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:24px;font-size:0.82rem;color:#b8900a;font-weight:600;">Not in RintiZ yet? Start here →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== BONUS STRUCTURE ===== -->
  <section id="bonus" class="py-24 px-6" style="background: #f5f5f5;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="fade-up text-center mb-16">
        <p style="color:#D4AF37;font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;">Monthly Bonus Structure</p>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); color: #111; line-height: 1.15;">The numbers. No fluff.</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: #777; margin-top: 12px; max-width: 560px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Every month you hit your AFYC target and 3 cases, NGM pays you a bonus — on top of the commission you already earned. Five tiers. You decide which one to aim for.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Monthly bonus table -->
      <div class="fade-up" style="background: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e8e8e8; box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
        <div style="overflow-x: auto;">
          <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            <thead>
              <tr style="background: #0C1B33;">
                <th style="padding: 18px 24px; text-align: left; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Monthly AFYC Target</th>
                <th style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Cases</th>
                <th style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #D4AF37;">Month 1–6 Bonus</th>
                <th style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Month 7–12</th>
                <th style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Month 13–24</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr style="background: #0C1B33; border-top: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.2);">
                <td style="padding: 20px 24px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; color: #D4AF37;" class="tabular">RM 12,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 20px 20px; text-align: center; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 0.9rem;">3</td>
                <td style="padding: 20px 20px; text-align: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #D4AF37;" class="tabular">RM 16,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 20px 20px; text-align: center; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 0.9rem;" class="tabular">RM 12,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 20px 20px; text-align: center; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 0.9rem;" class="tabular">RM 10,000</td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
                <td style="padding: 18px 24px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #111;" class="tabular">RM 9,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;">3</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; color: #111;" class="tabular">RM 12,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;" class="tabular">RM 9,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;" class="tabular">RM 7,500</td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="background: #fafafa; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
                <td style="padding: 18px 24px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #111;" class="tabular">RM 7,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;">3</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; color: #111;" class="tabular">RM 9,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;" class="tabular">RM 7,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;" class="tabular">RM 5,500</td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
                <td style="padding: 18px 24px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #111;" class="tabular">RM 5,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;">3</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; color: #111;" class="tabular">RM 6,500</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;" class="tabular">RM 5,000</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;" class="tabular">RM 4,000</td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="background: #fafafa;">
                <td style="padding: 18px 24px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #111;" class="tabular">RM 3,500</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;">3</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; color: #111;" class="tabular">RM 4,500</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;" class="tabular">RM 3,500</td>
                <td style="padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; color: #777; font-size: 0.88rem;" class="tabular">RM 2,500</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 16px 24px; background: #fafafa; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.78rem; color: #999; line-height: 1.6;">AFYC = Annualized First Year Commission from Life, Family Takaful, and Personal Accident products. Commission earned from AFYC is separate from and in addition to these bonuses. Bonuses paid via GIRO on the 15th of the following month.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quarterly bonus callout -->
      <div class="fade-up" style="margin-top: 24px; background: #0C1B33; border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;">
        <div>
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom: 8px;">Plus, every quarter</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #D4AF37; font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">Quarterly bonuses stack on top.</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); margin-top: 8px; max-width: 440px;">Hit 9 cases and RM36,000 quarterly AFYC in your first two quarters? That's an additional <strong style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">RM48,000</strong> per quarter — on top of your monthly bonuses.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#apply" style="white-space:nowrap;padding:14px 28px;background:#D4AF37;color:#0C1B33;border-radius:999px;font-weight:700;font-size:0.88rem;text-decoration:none;flex-shrink:0;">I want in →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CAREER PATH ===== -->
  <section id="path" class="py-24 px-6" style="background: #ffffff;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="fade-up text-center mb-16">
        <p style="color:#D4AF37;font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;">Career Progression</p>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); color: #111; line-height: 1.15;">Where NGM fits in the bigger picture</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-up" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 0;">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div style="position:relative;padding:32px 28px;border:1px solid #e8e8e8;border-right:none;background:#fafafa;">
          <div style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;background:#f0f0f0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:0.85rem;color:#999;margin-bottom:16px;">1</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#bbb;margin-bottom:6px;">Part-Time</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.15rem;color:#111;margin-bottom:8px;">RintiZ</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#888;line-height:1.6;">Start flexible. Learn the products. Build your client base. No experience needed.</p>
          <a href="https://notbadlah.com" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:16px;font-size:0.78rem;color:#bbb;font-weight:600;">notbadlah.com →</a>
