            <svg class="faq-icon" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-left:16px;transition:transform 0.25s;"><path d="M4 6.5L9 11.5L14 6.5" stroke="#999" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" style="display:none;padding:0 24px 20px;font-size:0.88rem;color:#666;line-height:1.75;">
            NGM+ is a separate programme for experienced Financial Services professionals who join AIA as an income-replacement hire. It's not a promotion from NGM — it's a different entry track. If you're already a Financial Planner, Banker, or Financial Advisor, ask Charles about NGM+ at <a href="https://nextgenmillionaire-plus.notbadlah.com" style="color:#D4AF37;text-decoration:none;">nextgenmillionaire-plus.notbadlah.com</a>.
          </div>
        </div>

